<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Discoun3, [User Name]!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #003366;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        .header h2 {
            font-size: 26px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .content h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            color: #666;
            padding: 30px;
            font-size: 13px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome to Discoun3, <%= userName %>!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h3>Get ready to discover exclusive deals and services!</h3>
            <p>As part of the Discoun3 community, you have access to a wide range of services offered by our trusted
                merchants. It's your time to explore amazing deals, book services, and save big!</p>
            <p><strong>Whatâ€™s next?</strong> Browse our marketplace, check out all the categories, and start making
                secure purchases with just a click.</p>
            <a href="<%= marketplaceLink %>" class="button">Browse Services</a>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here for you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Discoun3 | All Rights Reserved</p>
            <p><a href="https://discoun3ree.com/unsubscribe">Unsubscribe</a> | <a
                    href="https://discoun3ree.com/support">Contact Support</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>